    <item>
      <title>SS: Sazen&amp;#8217;s Secret</title>
      <link>https://shikarito.wordpress.com/kusuriya-no-hitorigoto/ss-sazens-secret/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://shikarito.wordpress.com/kusuriya-no-hitorigoto/ss-sazens-secret/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Jul 2025 16:02:25 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;main class="wp-block-group is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow"&gt; &lt;div class="wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained"&gt;&lt;h1 class="wp-block-post-title"&gt;SS: Sazen&amp;#8217;s Secret&lt;/h1&gt;   &lt;div style="height:1px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;   &lt;/div&gt;   &lt;div class="entry-content wp-block-post-content is-layout-constrained wp-block-post-content-is-layout-constrained"&gt; &lt;p&gt;The sound of something falling on snow. Was it a dead body?&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;The man had stolen a horse from the stables and was fastening his loot to it. He had taken part in the Shi clan&amp;#8217;s insurrection. Of course, it wasn’t out of some lofty ambition. The man was a peasant–he only worked as a guard at the fortress to earn money for food.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;He was going to mount the horse and escape as soon as he could. What was he thinking, going to check to see what had fallen?&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;“&amp;#8230;My lady?”&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;The girl was buried in the soft snow. Unconscious. There was a hole in the chest area of her dress. The unending white snow piled over her.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Her name was Loulan. The daughter of the patriarch of the Shi clan, the leader of this insurrection. She had entered the inner palace to be the emperor’s concubine.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Was she dead? No, puffs of her breath coloured the air white.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;The man swallowed. The girl who had been summoned away by the person above the heavens was so dazzlingly beautiful to a peasant. Such a person was breathing weakly before his eyes.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;“&amp;#8230;Ngh.”&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;A pained sound slipped out. She seemed to be really weak.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;“Find her!&lt;em&gt; Find her&lt;/em&gt;!”&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;He heard voices. It was the lot who came to suppress the insurrection.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;The man panicked. If he didn’t hightail it out of here in time, he may well be decapitated. And yet, the fallen girl weighed on his mind. She would be discovered if he left her be. Even if she weren’t found, she would be buried in snow and freeze to death.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;The man clutched his head, groaned and then sighed. He hoisted the girl out of the snow and over his shoulder.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;“Sorry. It’s a little heavy, so bear with it.”&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;The man offloaded one of the items he stole. There was another thing he had, but he couldn’t get rid of those. He got on the horse with the girl in front of him and tugged the reins.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;The man regretted picking up the unexpected thing he found. In an empty hut, he opened her dress. He couldn’t leave her in wet clothes.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;The hut was for hunters before they entered the forest. Thanks to that, there was a pelt, which he could use to cover and warm her up.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;The girl’s, Loulan’s, chest was bruised blue-black. The hole in her dress was from a firearm. Be it luck, a silver hairstick had caught it.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;With hesitation, the man extended his hand to Loulan’s chest. While somehow keeping calm from the soft sensation, he checked the condition of her bones. Her ribs weren’t broken. However, she had a fever and looked like she was in pain. She had fallen in the snow. Since her physical energy had dropped, it wouldn’t be out of the ordinary for her to catch a cold.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;He wouldn’t be able to run far with a sick person in tow. He would be quickly found if he brought Loulan with him. Loulan was certainly the daughter of his former employer, but he didn’t have that much of a sense of duty to go that far. &lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Rather, he thought that having brought her to a hut where she wouldn’t be discovered was good enough.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;It was snowing outside. The snow probably won’t be stopping any time soon, but as he was used to long winters, he would have no trouble escaping in this environment by himself.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;“&amp;#8230;Can you, do me a favour?”&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;The man heard a hoarse voice. He turned around. Loulan, wrapped in the pelt, was awake.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;“Th-these books…”&amp;nbsp; In Loulan’s hand was an item the man had looted.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;The cloth bag was filled with thick books. When did she see them?&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;“Bring them… to the capital.”&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;“&amp;#8230;What are you saying?” he said.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;It was troubling that she was telling him to take them to the capital. The man was currently on the run because of the army that came from the very capital. Once it was known that he participated in the insurrection, he would be arrested.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;“I beg, of you…” She got up and bowed her head deeply. The woman who had slept with the emperor before was doing that.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;The man had a sex drive that was like anyone else. A beautiful woman was bowing her head before him like this. There was no one to stop him, and the woman wouldn’t be able to defy him either.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;He could do whatever he wanted.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;… were the vulgar thoughts that crossed his mind. Just for a moment.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;“For the sake of this country…” Her voice was feeble. And yet, her eyes were bright with a burning fervour.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;For the sake of this country…&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;What an odd thing to say. Wasn’t she the daughter of the ringleader who tried to bring down the country?&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;However, the man was overpowered by the sparkle in her eyes. Overpowered by a woman who was much weaker than he, who was known as the ephemeral palace*.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="has-text-align-center"&gt;&lt;sub&gt;*probably a pun from Loulan&amp;#8217;s name. Lou &amp;gt; Palace (Roukaku), but ephemeral.&lt;/sub&gt; &lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;“I, I got it.”&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;At the same time that naturally came out of his mouth, Loulan collapsed in relief.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;He treated her with what he learnt by imitation. In the end, he couldn’t abandon her and waited until Loulan got better. &lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;He entered the forest and looked for medicinal herbs. Previously, he had been at a place where he had gathered medicinal herbs as an errand boy. He somehow kept his eyes on the goal, dug up the snow and found it. He had the doctor who had him work as the errand boy to teach him how to brew medicine.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;He made sure to light a fire at night. To keep warm, the two of them would sleep under the same pelt. It wasn’t that he didn’t get strange urges. But if he laid his hands on her, he had a feeling he would be the one eaten rather than the one eating.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;It wouldn’t be odd to describe her as a beauty who could bring a nation to ruin. Not her appearance, there was a quality to her that ordinary people didn&amp;#8217;t have.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;“Am I not attractive? I’m not flat either.”&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;As her health improved, she would make such jokes. Thanks to that, the man also spoke casually.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;After a short time, Loulan recovered greatly as well. Although the snow had yet to show signs of stopping, they decided to leave the hut.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;When they arrived at a village to the south that was quite some distance from the fortress, Loulan suggested they part ways.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;“I might end up selling the books, you know,” he said.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;“That can’t be helped since I can’t go to the capital. But it’s better than having the books burn with the fortress,” she said.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;“What will you do?”&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;There was nowhere for her to go. The world wasn’t so nice for a woman to escape alone.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;“I’m thinking of running further south.” Loulan grinned. “See ya. All the best.”&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;She turned her back on him without any reluctance to part.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;“Ah, that’s right. It would be nice if you could be a herbalist. It might be your calling.”&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;“No way.”&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;The laughing girl disappeared beyond the snow. He might never see her again.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;However, Loulan’s words resonated with him. He felt her words somehow became the source of encouragement for him to keep on living.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;That was exactly why he won&amp;#8217;t tell anyone, he thought.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;div id="jp-post-flair" class="sharedaddy sd-like-enabled"&gt;&lt;div class="sharedaddy sd-sharing-enabled"&gt;&lt;div class="robots-nocontent sd-block sd-social sd-social-official sd-sharing"&gt;&lt;h3 class="sd-title"&gt;Share this:&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;div class="sd-content"&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li class="share-facebook"&gt;&lt;div class="fb-share-button" data-href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/kusuriya-no-hitorigoto/ss-sazens-secret/" data-layout="button_count"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="share-end"&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class='sharedaddy sd-block sd-like jetpack-likes-widget-wrapper jetpack-likes-widget-unloaded' id='like-post-wrapper-130534757-5479-6905976ba1085' data-src='//widgets.wp.com/likes/index.html?ver=20251101#blog_id=130534757&amp;amp;post_id=5479&amp;amp;origin=shikarito.wordpress.com&amp;amp;obj_id=130534757-5479-6905976ba1085' data-name='like-post-frame-130534757-5479-6905976ba1085' data-title='Like or Reblog'&gt;&lt;div class='likes-widget-placeholder post-likes-widget-placeholder' style='height: 55px;'&gt;&lt;span class='button'&gt;&lt;span&gt;Like&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class='loading'&gt;Loading&amp;#8230;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span class='sd-text-color'&gt;&lt;/